{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hit the road in post-apocalyptic style!</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994660/extras/RPM_gif_03.gif?t=1721205782\" /><br><br>Get ready for a high-octane adventure in RPM - Road Punk Mayhem, a top-down vertical shoot\u2019em up that combines intense bullet hell mayhem with cel-shaded style! Inspired by arcade genre classics, RPM - Road Punk Mayhem lets you choose from 3 pilots of questionable sanity as you cruise through post-apocalyptic stages laying waste to enemy vehicles.<br><br>From tanks and helicopters to armored jets and monster trucks, your opponents won\u2019t pull any stops as they try to destroy your little fighter craft. Pick up fuel and warp-enabling stopwatches to keep moving, combo your way to huge score multipliers and use bombs to clear roadblocks! How long can you survive the wastelands? Challenge online leaderboards and push your damage-dealing skills to the limit!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994660/extras/RPM_gif_08.gif?t=1721205782\" /><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience intense bullet hell mayhem across post-apocalyptic stages!<br></li><li>Choose from 3 pilots, each with a unique ship and signature armaments.<br></li><li>Pick up fuel tanks to keep moving and stopwatches to enable warp!<br></li><li>Execute combos to increase your score multiplier!<br></li><li>Challenge online leaderboards!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hunter I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994660/48a2f1d265ec32f99567cc3a17333a628cec6541.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2994660/a2f843a14e5969eaaaf5990a1770049f0b4281c0.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/a